"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"PancakeSwap is the largest decentralized exchange on the Coin Smartchain (BSC). This article demonstrates how to make MetaMask work with PancakeSwap to trade NOC tokens.\\n\\n## 1. Prepare a wallet\\n\\nNaturally, if you want to trade on PancackeSwap, a BSC-enabled wallet is essential.\\n\\nSince BSC is compatible with the EVM virtual machine of ETH, you can also trade on PancackeSwap using MetaMask, but you need to add a BSC node to MetaMask first, here is the tutorial for adding a BSC node to MetaMask.\\n\\n[https://academy.binance.com/en/articles/connecting-metamask-to-binance-smart-chain](https://academy.binance.com/en/articles/connecting-metamask-to-binance-smart-chain)\\n\\nThis article uses the MetaMask wallet for demonstration, and the process for other wallets is similar, so I won't go over it again.\\n\\n## 2. Add NOC Token\\n\\n* Open PancakeSwap.\\n\\n  [https://pancakeswap.finance/swap](https://pancakeswap.finance/swap)\\n\\n* Click `Select a currency`.\\n\\n![Click Select a currency](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/LDNhLB9bC-u7WRguHgweF.png?height=840&width=730)\\n\\n* Click `Manage Tokens`.\\n\\n![Click Manage Tokens.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/F4ttD7C7obvNRnTB5mLRL.png?height=998&width=671)\\n\\n* Click on `Tokens` and enter the contract address of the NOC token:\\n\\n  `0x0e6457233baA6477F660666624Dc29d8e88d9fdf`\\n\\n![Enter the contract address](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FcvooigYFdsGQP9jpe_Zs.png?height=464&width=657)\\n\\n* After entering the contract address, the NOC token will pop up automatically, click `Import`.\\n\\n![Click Import](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/OpxyUHVcErh-hbBZnBNv4.png?height=601&width=677)\\n\\n* Check the `I understand` box, and then click `Import`.\\n\\n![Click Import](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JKsiEFgAqWaNZiZHlPiZH.png?height=820&width=638)\\n\\n* At this point, you can see that the NOC has been selected.\\n\\n![NOC](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pLdhkKA7rTWrD8gFrNHah.png?height=817&width=680)\\n\\n## 3. Connect with PancakeSwap\\n\\n* Click `Connect Wallet`.\\n\\n![Connect Wallet](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/W_NW_gWOS0b2U-H4PgfUg.png?height=829&width=735)\\n\\n* Click `MetaMask`\\n\\n![Click Metamask](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/-iKCCHttuhTRPO9CcnQl2.png?height=711&width=536)\\n\\n* A window will pop up, click Next (In English).\\n\\n![Click Next (In English)](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ZubBksxla7arW4onitmbA.png?height=919&width=519)\\n\\n* Click Connect and the window will close automatically after a successful connection.\\n\\n![Connect Wallet](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/VJbXxmwOqn4gXx9sX64pL.png?height=919&width=518)\\n\\n## 4. Set the appropriate pairs, slippage, etc.\\n\\n* Click on the location as shown in the image and change the currency to USDT.\\n\\n![Choose Token](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/OPicyKNJxDMm8BVPWAM8B.png?height=824&width=719)\\n\\n![Choose USDT](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/8xdaAOJMyx1ZtZUg1SkYz.png?height=960&width=649)\\n\\n* Click `Select a currency` and change the currency to NOC.\\n\\n![Select a currency](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Cs4xIFnmWvviXcaWixKYC.png?height=813&width=670)\\n\\n![Choose NOC](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/n-MAo7rUFIvz0zzMmOnoZ.png?height=968&width=641)\\n\\n* Click the gear in the upper right corner and set the slippage to 1%.\\n\\n![Click the gear](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/Zu78kia9wuqVbuKpKtsoX.png?height=826&width=713)\\n\\n![Set the slippage](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/lqf8atBuhzGBZmVFQWa4X.png?height=1043&width=626)\\n\\n## 5. Trading NOC\\n\\n* Enter the number of USDTs you need to trade.\\n\\n![Enter the number of USDTs](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/FmXy4Rhby2ulBPtz4rFCa.png?height=1092&width=727)\\n\\n* Click `Enable USDT`.\\n\\n![Enable USDT](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/C9ItS9f82vurSPtTgXqzy.png?height=1082&width=700)\\n\\n* In this case, MetaMask will pop up a prompt, click Confirm.\\n\\n![Confirm](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jnQ7x8zrLXAnoOQBnOqEK.png?height=1016&width=539)\\n\\n* Click `Swap`.\\n\\n![Click Swap](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DP5py1DHH2GH4PqFrk5mk.png?height=1093&width=732)\\n\\n* Click `Confirm Swap`.\\n\\n![Confirm Swap](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/xnyMm8aSR73FGX47UrRgM.png?height=778&width=934)\\n\\n* In this case, MetaMask will pop up a prompt, click again to confirm.\\n\\n![Confirm](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/UTO4cboIMwZ19txUFn4K-.png?height=1115&width=596)\\n\\n* At this point, the web page will show that the transaction was submitted successfully, and a moment later it will indicate in the upper right corner that the transaction was successful.\\n\\n![Transaction Submitted](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/AREuXFxBC-CqXVjDDkSDY.png?height=787&width=517)\\n\\n![Successful transaction](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rssq9Qmlp4Ug5sTfa1S3a.png?height=164&width=616)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637934127,\"title\":\"How to trade NOC tokens at PancakeSwap?\"},\"digest\":\"gKcjZwEo-7n3azLZo58Vlz78A-6YhuexzJNUrfXkh0o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9609f9a9Fd11964997a33bD33d3Ec6E67DA278a2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"scF357nEKgHtd0pXNBKh8EYaA9GICmtC9fsPYhO4e3c\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"d7VZqwXKJLGHvGkQGw1hT3MUg2M_Iz-4wV-Xyj7gCO8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"jineBGktUEjMUsYfkFPic2sCr-ka0-T1ecgBosF3TVwpYb4qP8j1ZzMtwR59rDw7TppjjKoj5WrX9Ctk5aPNyg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb1fa3318e9e26fd686fda877e67fd32355abd569f3c158a